discs.title: Corvette
discs.description: The Corvette is the fastest class of distance drivers, Speed 14. With a high glide rating, the Corvette will get the distance you require.

discs.title: Destroyer
discs.description: This overstable distance driver is a great disc for beginners. If you love to throw sidearms, this disc is for you!

discs.title: Leopard3
discs.description: The Leopard3 is an understable fairway driver. This disc will fly however you want, so make sure to control your release angles.

discs.title: Aviar3
discs.description: The Aviar3 has comfortable grip for a putter. If you are looking for a straight controlled shot with a slight fade, throw the Aviar3.

discs.title: Ballista
discs.description: The Ballista is a great disc for beginners and experienced players. It is overstable and understable, which makes the Balista a must-have in your bag.

discs.title: Convict
discs.description: The Convict is a great straight disc with slight stability at the end of flight. Throw the Convict to weave around obstacles and watch your score increase.

discs.title: Felon
discs.description: This fairway driver is great disc for windy days. Great low-ceiling shot with good glide and strong finish.

discs.title: Deputy
discs.description: Need to improve your short game? Look no further! The Deputy is a consistent understable putter at a low speed.

discs.title: Force
discs.description: The Force is Discraft's fastest overstable distance driver. If you throw with force, you want this disc in your bag.

discs.title: Nuke
discs.description: The Nuke is one of the most popular distance drivers in the world. This fast flying driver has a thick rim and maintains max speed for a long time.

discs.title: Buzzz
discs.description: The Buzzz is consistent, reliable and stable disc that will fly exactly how you want it to. This disc can fly anyway you want if thrown hard enough.

discs.title: Luna
discs.description: The Luna is an overstable putter made popular by Paul McBeth. This putter flys straight and perfect for players who putt with a lot of confidence.
